      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a project with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. It shows its age and has its share of wear, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. If you\u2019re practical, handy, or just want a cheap set of wheels, this could be a great fit. Priced fairly and ready for its next chapter.",
