    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and good core mechanicals. Cosmetics show age and it\u2019s not a perfect example, but it starts up, moves out well, and offers a great foundation for a dependable daily, backup vehicle, or easy project. A practical, affordable way into transportation without spending big money.",
